'''Ben Weyts''' (born 12 November 1970 in [[Leuven]]) is a [[Belgium|Belgian]] politician and is affiliated to the [[New Flemish Alliance|N-VA]]. He entered the [[Belgian Chamber of Representatives]] replacing [[Herman Van Rompuy]] on 31 December 2008 and was reelected in 2010.<ref>[http://www.dekamer.be/kvvcr/showpage.cfm?section=/depute&language=nl&rightmenu=right_depute&cfm=cvview53.cfm?key=01283&lactivity=52 Chamber of Representatives: cv Ben Weyts (Dutch)]</ref>
